 ('1', '71', 'en_us', '<h2>Faith and Works</h2><p>From the time of our founding in the mid 19th century, our motto has remained Fides Opera (Faith and Works). Our faith is expressed in the depth of resplendent worship, offering our very best in praise of God in the person of Jesus Christ. From this worship flows an outward ministry of works to a city and world crying for mindful and responsive hands, feet, and hearts.  </p>\n<p>“In God, that which is ancient never becomes old,” and we embrace this sentiment combining traditional liturgical worship with a radical inclusiveness deeply rooted in our parish’s history and celebrated by a vibrant diocese in which we serve.  Please consider this parish as you look for a spiritual home. All are welcome.</p>\n<p>With loving wishes, </p>\n<p>Fr. John David van Dooren<br />Rector</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-28 12:21:29', '2017-08-31 12:14:10', '4efea349-f217-4160-85b7-fb6fad4d8eea'),
 ('6', '88', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Leadership', '2017-08-28 19:41:48', '2017-08-31 14:47:18', '0e26c93d-dfb4-4626-ab43-0a809e7e7f98'),
 ('7', '233', 'en_us', '<blockquote>The Church of the Transfiguration is a community committed to faith in action. We embrace all who seek God’s inclusive love.</blockquote>\n<p>Erat purus ante habitasse mus interdum scelerisque a hac fermentum cum conguesuspendisse scelerisque auctor condimentum eu ipsum varius cursus a tempus aenean consectetur et a. Cubilia scelerisque ligula fusce a consequat vel fames a arcu mi nisl et at ultrices nunc. Sem inceptos sociosqu interdum adipiscing quis aliquam adipiscing vel taciti enim penatibus et ullamcorper venenatis.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-31 20:27:10', '2017-08-31 20:27:10', '40355163-cd50-4b54-8cf1-7244b56ba30b'),
 ('8', '236', 'en_us', '<h2>Sem inceptos sociosqu interdum</h2>\n<p>Consequat orci a cum suspendisse pretium orci dui dapibus ultricies nisi vulputate erat a dui. Ultricies enim a ut per egestas augue dis ad tellus mus a hac ac a scelerisque ullamcorper eupraesent quisque adipiscing. Erat purus ante habitasse mus interdum scelerisque a hac fermentum cum conguesuspendisse scelerisque auctor condimentum eu ipsum varius cursus a tempus aenean consectetur et a. Cubilia scelerisque ligula fusce a consequat vel fames a arcu mi nisl et at ultrices nunc. Sem inceptos sociosqu interdum adipiscing quis aliquam adipiscing vel taciti enim penatibus et ullamcorper venenatis.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-31 20:29:51', '2017-08-31 20:29:51', '95a47034-3045-4f2f-a8c1-23423df1e32d'),
 ('9', '240', 'en_us', '<p>Sunday Coffee Hours also afford parishioners and newcomers opportunities to interact and to build relationships that often result in invitations to break bread or to take advantage of the many cultural events in New York. Fundraisers, like our Spring Music Gala, are also a great way to interact with fellow parishioners and to enjoy the talent and hospitality of our parish.</p>\n<p>Sign up for our <a href=\"http://lc-craft/grace/entries/about/new#\">weekly Friday blasts</a> and check <a href=\"http://lc-craft/grace/entries/about/new#\">our calendar</a> for upcoming events and opportunities to participate in the robust Parish Life of Church of the Transfiguration.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-31 20:36:16', '2017-09-01 09:33:22', 'a5bedbb0-9db6-4341-a650-1b3dead7ad93'),
 ('10', '245', 'en_us', '<p>At the center of our worship is emphasis on both Word and Table. Little Church clergy are considered <a href=\"#\">excellent preachers</a> who connect lectionary readings with Biblical context and current challenges with a smattering of personal stories and humor. Transfiguration acolytes do an extraordinary job in ensuring the Eucharist is celebrated with majesty and dignity, and the authentic expertise of <a href=\"#\">our choirs</a> draws worshippers closer to the love of Jesus Christ through some of the most beloved hymns of the Church.</p>\n<p>Below is the current worship schedule. Please consider joining us!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-01 10:13:16', '2017-09-01 10:13:52', '5a3b9ab1-6b50-436d-9ec0-0bda511fb980');
